metadata.name: Gothika Luxe - 1 of 15
metadata.description: Gothika Luxe is a limited edition NFT collection of 15 breathtaking images, each featuring a beautiful woman of color adorned in glamorous gothic clothing and surrounded by intricate floral elements. From dark, rich hues to delicate blooms, these photorealistic renders are a unique blend of beauty and edge, showcasing the strength and confidence of these women. These prints are a stunning addition to any art lover's collection. This collection is available in a limited run of 15 prints, making it a truly special and rare piece of art.
